<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='338457' id='t-338457'>And they visit each other to try to learn,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='341137' id='t-341137'>so a continuous cycle of improvement.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='344927' id='t-344927'>For many years, Swedish hip surgeons</span>
