</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:06
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='355035' id='t-355035'>Now I found this principle really exciting.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='357917' id='t-357917'>So the physicians get together,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='359720' id='t-359720'>they agree on what quality is,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='361845' id='t-361845'>they start measuring, they share the data,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='365559' id='t-365559'>they find who's best, and they learn from it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='369075' id='t-369075'>Continuous improvement.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:22
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='371667' id='t-371667'>Now, that's not the only exciting part.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='374215' id='t-374215'>That's exciting in itself.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='376466' id='t-376466'>But if you bring back the cost side of the equation,</span>
