<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='460738' id='t-460738'>of the healthcare budget of the country.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='463451' id='t-463451'>Now you may say that these numbers</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='465558' id='t-465558'>are fantastic, and it's all logical,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='468449' id='t-468449'>but is it possible?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='470459' id='t-470459'>This would be a paradigm shift in healthcare,</span>
