<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='516976' id='t-516976'>is no better than what others do,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='519830' id='t-519830'>they will do whatever it takes to improve.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='522537' id='t-522537'>But most of them don't know.</span>
