 9:24
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='553654' id='t-553654'>Now, you may say this is a nice idea,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='556595' id='t-556595'>but this isn't only an idea.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='558499' id='t-558499'>This is happening in reality.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='560527' id='t-560527'>We're creating a global community,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='563681' id='t-563681'>and a large global community,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='565544' id='t-565544'>where we'll be able to measure and compare</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='568091' id='t-568091'>what we achieve.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='569805' id='t-569805'>Together with two academic institutions,</span>
