<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='588183' id='t-588183'>for Health Outcome Measurement.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='591143' id='t-591143'>We're bringing together leading physicians</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='593892' id='t-593892'>and patients to discuss, disease by disease,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='597483' id='t-597483'>what is really quality,</span>
