<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='645216' id='t-645216'>Why is that?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:59
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='648267' id='t-648267'>Five months ago,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='651132' id='t-651132'>I led a workshop at the largest university hospital</span>
