<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:13
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='722925' id='t-722925'>By measuring value in healthcare,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='725012' id='t-725012'>that is not only costs</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='727037' id='t-727037'>but outcomes that matter to patients,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='729510' id='t-729510'>we will make staff in hospitals</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='731308' id='t-731308'>and elsewhere in the healthcare system</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='733167' id='t-733167'>not a problem but an important part of the solution.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='737261' id='t-737261'>I believe measuring value in healthcare</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='739197' id='t-739197'>will bring about a revolution,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='741968' id='t-741968'>and I'm convinced that the founder</span>
